  <summary>customize icons, xrdb and GTK themes</summary>
  <description>
      <p>Graphical application for generating different color variations of Oomox (Numix-based), Materia (ex-Flat-Plat) and Arc themes (GTK2, GTK3, Cinnamon, GNOME, Openbox, Xfwm), Archdroid, Gnome-Colors, Numix, Papirus, Suru++ icon themes. Have a hack for HiDPI in gtk2.</p>
      <p>WARNING: Oomox-spotify plugin is disabled for Flatpak because of isolation.</p>
